@lifeofartistpod
A podcast dedicated to sharing the raw, inspiring journeys of artists pursuing their passions. We dive into the dreams, challenges, and daily lives of creatives, as well as the crucial role mental health plays in following a calling. Featuring candid conversations with both artists and behind-the-scenes professionals, we aim to demystify the artist’s journey and celebrate the community that brings art to life.

Our mission: To inspire, connect, and create a space where the highs and lows of creative careers are shared openly, offering insight and encouragement to all who dare to follow their dreams.

